OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774954972
OL,3,CVideo captures 'teenagers' throwing
OL,4,Cmissiles at passing cars
OL,6,FFootage from Incident on Teesside and
OL,7,FCounty Durham circulated online at the
OL,8,Fweekend
OL,10,FPolice are investigating after a video
OL,11,Fcirculated online showing people
OL,12,Fthrowing missiles over a wall at
OL,13,Fpassing cars in Middlesbrough.
OL,15,FThe footage, believed to have been
OL,16,Ftaken on a street in North Ormesby
OL,17,Fover the weekend, appears to show
OL,18,Fthree individuals thought to be
OL,19,Fteenagers - two wearing balaclavas and
OL,20,Fone with their hood up.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
