CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774954972
OL,3,CVideo captures 'teenagers' throwing
OL,4,Cmissiles at passing cars
OL,6,FThe video was filmed by a passenger in
OL,7,Fa vehicle who shared it on social
OL,8,Fmedia as a warning to drivers in the
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FCleveland Police confirmed on Monday
OL,12,F(30 March) that the force is
OL,13,Finvestigating.
OL,15,FInspector Des Horton told ITV Tyne
OL,16,FTees there had been pockets of similar
OL,17,Fattacks in the area and warned the
OL,18,Faction is likely to land the
OL,19,Fperpetrators in court on very serious
OL,20,Fcharges.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
