PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1774954972
OL,3,CVideo captures 'teenagers' throwing
OL,4,Cmissiles at passing cars
OL,6,F"It's very shocking," he added.
OL,7,F"Frustratingly, I think some of these
OL,8,Fchildren see it as a little bit of
OL,9,Fnuisance behaviour or silliness of
OL,10,Ftheir behalf but the reality is it
OL,11,Fisn't.
OL,13,F"It's criminality at every level.
OL,14,FWhether you're throwing and you're
OL,15,Fmissing cars - whether you're hitting
OL,16,Fcars or whether you're causing injury
OL,17,F- every single aspect of that is
OL,18,Fcriminality."
OL,20,FThere were no reports of injury or
OL,21,Fdamage to any of the vehicles.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
